olding  Complete a Form W 4 in ink claiming exempt on Line 7  and do not write anything on Lines 5 or 6  A new form must be completed each year no later than 15 February  You are eligible to claim exempt only if you had no federal tax liability last year and expect to have none this year  How do I claim exempt from state income tax withholding  Complete a Form VA 4 checking the box for exempt  and do not write anything on Lines 1 or 2  A new form must be completed each year  as forms expire on 31 December  See VA 4 form instructions on back of form to determine if you are eligible to claim exempt  Hourly Timesheet When is my hourly wage timesheet due  Hourly wage timesheets are due by 5 00 pm on the 2nd business day after the end of the pay period  Payment for timesheets received after the deadline may be delayed until the following pay period  Please complete timesheets in ink and be sure that both the employee and the supervisor initial any corrections  Where do I send my hourly wage timesheet  Send to Payroll  311 Smith Hall  through Post Mail or hand deliver before the due date  Direct Deposit Changes How do I change my direct deposit  Remember that direct deposit is required for payroll  Notify us immediately if there is a change in your account  Any change requires a new Employee Electronic Direct Deposit Authorization form  as the new form replaces the old one  If possible  attach a voided check or copy of a check  NOT a deposit slip  for each new account listed on the form  If you do not have a voided check available  you may write in the banking routing number and your account number  but any errors may delay your pay  Please complete the form in ink and send to Payroll  311 Smith Hall  at least two weeks before the payday on which you wish it to take effect  Address Changes How do I change the address on my paycheck or W 2  Contact the VMI Human Resourses Office as soon as possible when you have an address change  Cadets should contact the Registrar s Office  W 2 When will I receive my Form W 2  Form W 2s are mailed to employees no later than 31 January Tax Shelter Enrollment or Changes How do I enroll in or change an existing 457 or 403b deferred compensation  tax shelter  plan  Contact the Human Resources Office  Payroll Deductions Can I have my VMI Foundation or VMI Keydet Club contributions deducted from my pay  Yes  Mail a completed Alumni Agencies Payroll Deduction Authorization form to Payroll  311 Smith Hall at least two weeks before the payday on which you wish it to take effect  Health Care Is there a list of health care codes and the employee cost  Yes  Click on COVA Codes to display codes  code descriptions  and the Employee and Employer Amounts  Payroll Office Payroll Home Access to Pay Info  Pay Schedule FAQs Payroll Staff VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 